# Peruvian-Style White Beans

Based on [https://www.goya.com/en/recipes/peruvian-style-beans](https://www.goya.com/en/recipes/peruvian-style-beans) and [https://www.thespruceeats.com/peruvian-beans-3029292](https://www.thespruceeats.com/peruvian-beans-3029292)

